title: Urf the Nami-tee Bug
body: In the "Urf the Nami-tee" skin for Nami, one of the Sharks/Manatees has, what looks to be, the shark (from the original skin) fused with the manatee, is there any chance that this could be fixed?

replies.body:
Hey pkcrory,

Thanks for the report! You're right, it's pulling both models. We'll get this fixed up!
